examples.en: I was nearly deafened by the loud music.
examples.ru: Я чуть не оглох от такой громкой музыки.

examples.en: We were deafened by the explosion.
Our voices were deafened with the noise of the sea.
The sound of the musketry had deafened them to everything else.
examples.ru: Из-за шума мушкетных выстрелов они ничего не слышали.
